{"tid":1609292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人記得10月10號呢個日子？呢日比10月1號更加有意思！","createTime":"2019-10-01T14:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T15:48:38.000Z","uid":126352,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"f21092fac2bbe8033744a33e00de206572bbc79f","tid":1609292,"uid":126352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:13:38.000Z","msg":"今日係國殤日相信唔使我講大家都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係...真係冇人記得10月10號？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其實10月10號嘅意義更加重大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n係108年前嘅10月10號，就係辛亥革命嘅開始，當年最終成功推翻左滿清，建立咗中華民國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OirWtL7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOirWtL7.png&h=6790772e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YoMn8L7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYoMn8L7.png&h=e819e4eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係108年之後嘅10月10號，香港人係咪可以做返啲嘢去<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">紀念</span>呢個日子?<br />\n<br />\n如果呢一日全香港人都舉起<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">青天白日滿地紅旗</span>慶祝雙十，習大大應該會激到跳起？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以提議下嗰日慶祝活動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21d637df8df6fa8d19d79bbe252b4f9c0f94d21","tid":1609292,"uid":134466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:15:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a99cf46ab04c2b528e62edc5331b260698bddcaf","tid":1609292,"uid":185184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:16:13.000Z","msg":"出街歡呼得啦掛"},{"pid":"dff8d698c043dca0813c191ae8c63660675d568e","tid":1609292,"uid":126352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:16:17.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c41851f59ad1d42f2ace657555473b001608335c","tid":1609292,"uid":201816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:17:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d211297a3d1189c936b0e1dcc0a65dd0f6fe608a","tid":1609292,"uid":94502,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"不如搞掂10月9天崎上訴先？"},{"pid":"c03a1a2638c815d781ee8b3c22b87c228df51cb6","tid":1609292,"uid":94502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d211297a3d1189c936b0e1dcc0a65dd0f6fe608a","tid":1609292,"uid":94502,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"不如搞掂10月9天崎上訴先？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:18:16.000Z","msg":"*琦"},{"pid":"5a90726f0e4190453811cc747bc45ef2d9a10a9b","tid":1609292,"uid":48315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:18:18.000Z","msg":"雙十緊係出去狂歡啦<br />\n一定要落撚哂中共面屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8f93307d20d02721edfcba4372714ba013d67d","tid":1609292,"uid":126352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:20:06.000Z","msg":"10/10 雙十節<br />\n香港人係咪要做啲嘢紀念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7789fb54ffcc25df1b512af0485f0abef42d37f","tid":1609292,"uid":126352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14